LookSmart,provides,search,marketing,via,its,pay,per,click,search,advertising,network,The,LookSmart,AdCenter,API,makes,data,and,functionality,available,to,advertisers,outside,of,the,AdCenter,website,Developers,can,manage,large,or,complex,advertising,campaigns,programmatically,The,API,allows,developers,to,create,and,change,campaigns,and,advertisements,Further,the,API,can,be,used,to,integrate,with,internal,reporting,billing,and,inventory,management,systems,The,API,uses,SOAP,Documentation,is,available,upon,request